name: Mibio
tag_list: tech, startup, nashville, cloud-storage, ios, iphone, mobile
overview:
Everyone loves to relive their memories, but in order to relive better we need to capture better.

Mibio helps you capture life experiences with way more than just photos.

Mibio allows you to capture and collect media and information to build a rich memory as it happens. It lets you capture photos, video, and audio; pull in data and posts from your social networks, and make the story smarter by adding in your location, weather, and people involved. The system gets smarter over time knowing when you are away from home on a trip or when its time to document important events.

Mibio automatically organizes and stores all of the original media in the cloud allowing easy social publishing, book printing and easily downloadable.
